-- China Electric Cars Strategic Industry in 5-Year Plan: Wan Gang
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-11-06T07:18:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-06/china-electric-cars-strategic-industry-in-5-year-plan-minister-wan-says.html
China’s electric cars are a
“strategic industry” under the country’s next five-year plan
and parts makers will receive tax breaks and subsidies similar
to traditional automakers, Wan Gang, the nation’s Science and
Technology Minister, said at a forum in Shenzhen.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Allen Wan at 
 awan3@bloomberg.net  